Dear Professor Goodwin,
Yes, we added carbon to the atoms list, but we found out that the 
error was due to Windows. Not because of Cantera. My supervisor 
Arief Dahoe discovered it after I left yesterday and fixed it.
And now, he wants to replace Windows by Linux in fireSert.
Thanks for your help.
Yours sincerely,
Solene
